      • Tickets

        public Tickets(int id,
       java.lang.String nom,
       java.lang.String desc,
       java.lang.String dateCrea,
       java.lang.String dateDerniereMod,
       java.lang.String nomDemandeur,
       java.lang.String etat)
        This is the constructor to make a ticket. You should not have to use it, as the tickets are already created by other methods located in GlpiConnector They are usually directly found in the GLPI DB
        Parameters:
        id - Id of the ticket
        nom - Name of the ticket
        desc - Description of the problem
        dateCrea - Date where the ticket was created
        dateDerniereMod - Last time it was modified
        nomDemandeur - Name of the person who made the ticket
        etat - Status of the ticket
